{"type": "article", "id": 26550, "title": "窈窕淑椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-09T06:56:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162016kcwrlivNtXAVdF3E.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">这一系列利用了木材与圆钢的椅子有一个非常形象的名字叫“窈窕淑椅”，由<a href=\"http://www.deshaus.com/\">大舍建筑设计事务所</a>设计。一根完整的圆钢经过弯曲后组成了把手、椅背和后腿，而圆形且微微弯曲的座椅和前腿则由木材这一传统的家具材料所制成。两者组合后形成了一种鲜明的反差，看似纤细但并不脆弱。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162014QIoyTx9KZlk6bgLE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162015qvkQysIwdUpLJrFE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162015Z09fCqBonW5gdNVk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37604167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021620167QEuzKgA9hyJbfdB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}